---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Barrana Accounting Services | CPA-led accounting for Ontario businesses"
  description="Learn how Barrana Accounting Services combines CPA oversight with a more organised accounting delivery model for Ontario SMBs."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="overline about-hero__overline">Our story</p>
      <h1>Built for businesses that want a more organised accounting experience</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__body">Barrana Accounting Services brings together professional accounting oversight and operational workflow thinking to support Ontario businesses with bookkeeping, tax, payroll, reporting, and advisory work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin story -->
  <section class="section about-origin">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-origin__grid">
        <div class="about-origin__text fade-in">
          <h2>Why we built Barrana Accounting Services</h2>
          <p>Barrana.ai has worked with businesses on workflow improvement and automation across a range of operational functions. Over time, one pattern kept showing up: accounting work was often being handled through processes that felt more reactive, fragmented, and manual than they needed to be.</p>
          <p>Business owners were not only looking for bookkeeping, tax, payroll, and reporting. They were also looking for a smoother way to manage recurring tasks, requests, deadlines, and handoffs.</p>
          <p>Barrana Accounting Services was created to bring those two needs together: professional accounting support led by a licensed CPA, delivered through a more organised and modern operating model.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-origin__visual fade-in">
          <div class="org-card">
            <div class="org-card__inner">
              <p class="org-card__label">Workflow and automation expertise</p>
              <p class="org-card__name">Barrana.ai</p>
              <p class="org-card__desc">Operational workflow design and systems support</p>
              <a href="https://barrana.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="org-card__link">barrana.ai &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="org-card__connector" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="org-card__plus">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="org-card__inner org-card__inner--accent">
              <p class="org-card__label org-card__label--light">CPA-led accounting support</p>
              <p class="org-card__name">Barrana Accounting Services</p>
              <p class="org-card__desc org-card__desc--light">Accounting for Ontario businesses</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we believe -->
  <section class="section about-beliefs" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-in">
        <h2>What we believe good accounting service should feel like</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="beliefs-grid">
        <div class="belief-block fade-in">
          <h3 class="belief-block__title">Clear communication</h3>
          <p class="belief-block__body">Clients should know what is happening with their file without having to ask.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="belief-block fade-in">
          <h3 class="belief-block__title">Consistent process</h3>
          <p class="belief-block__body">Recurring work should run on a predictable rhythm, not be driven by deadlines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="belief-block fade-in">
          <h3 class="belief-block__title">Professional review</h3>
          <p class="belief-block__body">Technology can handle repetitive tasks. A CPA should handle the judgment calls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="belief-block fade-in">
          <h3 class="belief-block__title">Better visibility for the client</h3>
          <p class="belief-block__body">Good accounting gives you clearer numbers, not just compliance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section about-team">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-in">
        <h2>The people behind the service</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Replace before launch -->
        <div class="team-card fade-in">
          <div class="team-card__avatar" aria-hidden="true">CPA</div>
          <div class="team-card__content">
            <div class="team-card__name-row">
              <h3 class="team-card__name">[CPA Partner Name]</h3>
              <span class="team-card__badge">CPA, CGA</span>
            </div>
            <p class="team-card__role">Accounting Partner</p>
            <p class="team-card__bio">[Placeholder bio — 2 sentences about background and specialty. Replace before launch with real credentials and experience.]</p>
            <p class="team-card__note">PLACEHOLDER — add real bio and credentials before launch</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card fade-in">
          <div class="team-card__avatar" aria-hidden="true">B</div>
          <div class="team-card__content">
            <div class="team-card__name-row">
              <h3 class="team-card__name">Barrana.ai</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="team-card__role">Systems and workflow support</p>
            <p class="team-card__bio">Barrana's experience in workflow design supports how the accounting service is delivered, especially where recurring tasks, handoffs, and communication structure can be made more efficient.</p>
            <a href="https://barrana.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="team-card__link">Learn more at Barrana.ai &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Barrana.ai connection -->
  <section class="section about-connection" style="background: var(--color-dark);">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <h2 style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">How Barrana.ai supports the service</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
          Barrana Accounting Services benefits from Barrana.ai's experience in workflow design and operational systems. That support helps improve how the accounting service is delivered, especially where recurring tasks, handoffs, and communication structure can be made more efficient.
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); line-height: 1.8;">
          That does not change the core model of the service. Accounting work still depends on professional review, context, and judgment. The technology and workflow layer exists to support that work, not replace it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner
    heading="Want to see whether this approach fits your business?"
    body="Book a consultation to discuss your accounting needs and how we work."
    cta1Label="Book a consultation"
    cta1Href="/contact/"
    cta2Label="See how it works"
    cta2Href="/how-it-works/"
  />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(126, 15, 74, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
    padding-block: var(--space-20) var(--space-24);
  }

  .about-hero__overline {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-hero__body {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    max-width: 580px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Origin */
  .about-origin {
    background: var(--color-light);
  }

  .about-origin__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-origin__text h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-origin__text p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .org-card {
    background: var(--color-dark-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .org-card__inner {
    padding: var(--space-8);
  }

  .org-card__inner--accent {
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .org-card__label {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .org-card__label--light {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .org-card__name {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .org-card__desc {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .org-card__desc--light {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  }

  .org-card__link {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .org-card__link:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .org-card__connector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-block: var(--space-2);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .org-card__plus {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  /* Beliefs */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .beliefs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .belief-block {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .belief-block__title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .belief-block__body {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Team */
  .about-team {
    background: var(--color-light);
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .team-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .team-card__avatar {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .team-card__name-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .team-card__name {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .team-card__badge {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(126, 15, 74, 0.1);
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .team-card__role {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .team-card__bio {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .team-card__note {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .team-card__link {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .team-card__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-origin__grid,
    .team-grid,
    .beliefs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
